'''Aƒlao''' alo '''Aflao''' enye du si le [[Ghana]] kpakple [[Togo]] woƒe liƒo dzi. Eŋlisiawo yɔna du sia be '[[:en:Aflao|Aflao]]'.

== Aƒlao ƒe nɔƒe ==
Aƒlao le Ketu South Distrikt me le [[Volta Region]] le Ghana. Distrikt la ƒe toxɔ du ye enye [[Denu]]. Togo nye dukɔ si le Ghana ƒe ɣedzeƒe kpa dzi eye [[Lome]] enye du si le Togo dukɔ me. [[Eʋegbe|Eʋeawo]] ƒe duwo demetɔ ɖekae nye Aƒlao. 
Aƒlao nye du mamlɛ tɔ sime na to hafi a geɖe [[Togo]] me.

== Kluvi si ==
Le blemaŋɔli la, Aƒlao nye kluvi si gãtɔ ɖeka. <ref>Dickson, K. B. "Trade Patterns in Ghana at the Beginning of the Eighteenth Century." Geographical Review 56.3 (1966): 417-431</ref> Asi gã aɖe gale Aƒlao fifia eye wodzrana nuvovowo le afima.<ref>[http://www.ghana-pedia.org/org/index.php?option=com_directory&listing=Aflao&page=viewListing&lid=228&Itemid=36 Aflao on Ghana-Pedia]</ref>

